                    </div>
                    <span>Great animal pictures. One dog looked like a girl I knew. But the poems/captions seem rather trite and contrived. Its a nice coffee table book, but somewhat cheesy. I read it at my aunt's house. Otherwise, I wouldn't buy it.</span>
                  
              
